# Stock Market App Project Summary

## Overview
This is a comprehensive stock market tracking application built with the modern Next.js 15 App Router. It allows users to track their favorite stocks, view real-time market data, and read financial news.

## Technology Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js 15 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4, Shadcn UI, Radix UI primitives, Lucide React icons
- **Database:** MongoDB configured with Mongoose ORM
- **Authentication:** `better-auth` for secure user login and registration flows
- **Background Jobs:** Inngest SDK for handling asynchronous or scheduled background tasks
- **Email:** Nodemailer for automated email communications

## Key Features & Integrations
1. **Real-time Market Data & Charts:** 
   The application heavily integrates with **TradingView widgets** for interactive visual data. The dashboard ([app/(root)/page.tsx](file:///Users/dhawaljain/Documents/Stock%20market%20app/stock_market/stock-tracker/app/%28root%29/page.tsx)) features:
   - Market Overview
   - Stock Heatmap
   - Financial News Timeline
   - Market Quotes

2. **Stock Search & Market News (Finnhub API):**
   Server actions in [lib/actions/finnhub.actions.ts](file:///Users/dhawaljain/Documents/Stock%20market%20app/stock_market/stock-tracker/lib/actions/finnhub.actions.ts) securely leverage the **Finnhub API** to provide:
   - Specific company news and broad market news
   - Stock symbol search functionality
   - Fallback display for top popular stocks (e.g., Apple, Tesla)

3. **Personalized Watchlists:**
   Fully implemented backend schema ([database/models/watchlist.model.ts](file:///Users/dhawaljain/Documents/Stock%20market%20app/stock_market/stock-tracker/database/models/watchlist.model.ts)) that links stock symbols to user accounts securely, preventing duplicates, and allowing users to maintain a persistent catalog of targeted companies.

4. **Omnibar Search Component:**
   Features a quick command menu ([searchCommand.tsx](file:///Users/dhawaljain/Documents/Stock%20market%20app/stock_market/stock-tracker/components/searchCommand.tsx) utilizing `cmdk`) for rapid stock lookups across the platform.
